{"tid":1319030,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"預防瘋狗症，散水珠仔陣","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T11:26:03.000Z","uid":238013,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"213952daba6cfcbd43252eb4e7811846b4330e43","tid":1319030,"uid":238013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:27:33.000Z","msg":"經過尋日發生的狗帶脫索，癲狗衝入商場咬人事件，相信大家都未能平復。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NVWsvKj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNVWsvKj.jpg&h=bf6bad02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇過唔少片，好多癲狗即使全副武裝， 加上近日又怕畀人影到個樣眼罩貼反光貼紙，視野受護目鏡阻礙， 經常被地上嘅障礙物跣倒，諗到一個令佢地減低衝擊的障礙 / 減慢追捕速度<br />\n<br />\n之前我都有諗過捉波子棋， 可惜數量有限而且相對成本較高。<br />\n<br />\n近排細妹迷上穿<span style=\"color: blue;\">珠仔</span>，發現深水埗有好多好平 嘅珠仔， 嗰日喺舖頭唔覺意到寫咗一盤珠仔，差啲跣低曬周圍的客人，搞到我地勁唔好意思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講咗咁耐 下面個導賞介紹好有用：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.guideguide.hk/%E3%80%90%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%8F%E8%A1%97%E3%80%91diy%E6%89%8B%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82-%E7%8F%A0%E4%BB%94%E8%A1%97-%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.guideguide.hk%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E6%2589%258B%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%25A1%2597%25E3%2580%2591diy%25E6%2589%258B%25E4%25BD%259C%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E7%258F%25A0%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%25A1%2597-%25E6%258E%25A2%25E7%25B4%25A2%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259A%2584%25E9%259D%25A2%2F&d=Nl%2Bce6%2FxXxAB2W4e8qnvdt5k9s62d79lhUbErROZgj4%3D&h=6e7cf707\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.guideguide.hk/%E3%80%90%E6%89%8B%E5%B7%A5%E5%B0%8F%E8%A1%97%E3%80%91diy%E6%89%8B%E4%BD%9C%E5%A4%A9%E5%A0%82-%E7%8F%A0%E4%BB%94%E8%A1%97-%E6%8E%A2%E7%B4%A2%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82%E4%B8%8D%E5%90%8C%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%A2/</a>"},{"pid":"080e34b97b2c5406cbfbe8614da4ba2ca2f977fb","tid":1319030,"uid":79563,"like":7,